  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Test, TestEnvironment

    public class RemoveLookupLocatorsFiniteFromEmpty
extends RemoveLookupLocators
    This class determines whether or not the lookup discovery service can successfully remove a set of locators from the set of locators with which it has been configured to join. This test attempts to remove a non-empty set of locators from the empty set of locators with which the service is currently configured.
    See Also:
